code: // -------------------- Static methods -------------------------------------- public static ResourceManagerRuntimeServices fromConfiguration(ResourceManagerRuntimeServicesConfiguration configuration, HighAvailabilityServices highAvailabilityServices, ScheduledExecutor scheduledExecutor) throws Exception {     final SlotManagerConfiguration slotManagerConfiguration = configuration.getSlotManagerConfiguration().     final SlotManager slotManager = new SlotManager(scheduledExecutor, slotManagerConfiguration.getTaskManagerRequestTimeout(), slotManagerConfiguration.getSlotRequestTimeout(), slotManagerConfiguration.getTaskManagerTimeout()).     final JobLeaderIdService jobLeaderIdService = new JobLeaderIdService(highAvailabilityServices, scheduledExecutor, configuration.getJobTimeout()).     return new ResourceManagerRuntimeServices(slotManager, jobLeaderIdService). }
